Numeric

ntri                  Generate triangular numers.
scale0                Scale numeric vectors.

Conversions

squarematrix          Transorm to squared matrix.
enpaire               Generate a pairwise list.

Data and System

gapply                Apply a function on a data.frame by a grid.
as.data.frame, as.data.table
                      Convert gapply results back to data.frames.
textable              Create a latex document containing a table.
lload                 Load objects from R data files into a list.
lsall, rmall          List details from and remove all objects.

Strings and Pattern

leading0              Prepend zeroes to unify number lengths.
strextr               Extract substrings by pattern.
strpart               Extract substrings by splitting.
strrev                Reverse strings.
msub, mgsub           Multiple pattern replacement.
gregexprind           Get index of expression.
mgrepl                Multiple pattern search.

Graphics

gghcl                 Create a color palette.
ggplotlist            Plot a list containing ggplot objects.